node.text:
Folks, we have a real crisis at our border. We shot this footage at 1AM in the border town of Roma, Texas. Please watch and share.

Leaders go to the frontlines to assess a problem. Leaders lead 24/7, being a governor is not a 9-5 job. 

This crisis at our border is one of the reasons I am fighting for you. Will you join me in Defending the Texas Republic?

node.text:
Not only is Texas leading the nation in human and sex trafficking, but due to the unconstitutional draconian lockdown, Texas leads the nation in Chapter 11 bankruptcies. 

For each 10,000 businesses in Texas, 22.85 filed for Chapter 11. Rounding out the top five states filing Chapter 11 are New York, Delaware, and Virginia. 

I think this is a good indicator of what the lockdown and closure of "non-essential businesses" did to our state. This is not what #TexasFirst means to a Governor West. #bankruptcy

It is revealing that a sitting governor would commission such a poll after we've barely hit the two-week mark since announcing our campaign.

I do wonder how many people along the Texas border were polled as to who they would like to see uphold the rule of law in the state of Texas. 

It is encouraging to know that our campaign has been validated by @governorabbott Abbott’s team.
